channel.title: What's a Hamachi?
channel.description: I have hamachi, I connect with it, I have no idea why, or what I'm doing when I do connect to it. Whats it for? Does it matter? Is it like another version of Mopar some how? Hamachi guide - detailed for the new guy please :confused:

item.title: What's a Hamachi?
item.dc:creator: @mrrules mrrules
item.description:
@mrrules wrote:

Find out someone’s network name and pass and go to the button on the lower right hand corner and push join netowork and put in that network name and pass , then use the ip beside the hoster and use it to join there server.
